Get an election's raw supplemental questionnaire data

Source: R/fokus.gen.R
raw_q_suppl_election.Rd

Returns a structured list of an election's data from the canton's political-level-specific raw supplemental date-specific FOKUS questionnaire data.

raw_q_suppl_election(
  ballot_date = all_ballot_dates,
  lvl = all_lvls,
  canton = all_cantons,
  prcd = all_prcds,
  election_nr = 1L
)

Arguments

ballot_date

FOKUS-covered ballot date. One of

  • "2018-09-23"

  • "2018-11-25"

  • "2019-10-20"

  • "2020-09-27"

  • "2020-10-18"

  • "2021-11-28"
lvl

Political level. One of

  • "cantonal"

  • "federal"
canton

Canton name. One of

  • "aargau"
prcd

Election procedure. One of

  • "proportional"

  • "majoritarian"
election_nr

Election number. A positive integerish scalar.

Value

A strict list.

Examples

fokus:::raw_q_suppl_election(ballot_date = "2019-10-20",
                             lvl = "cantonal",
                             canton = "aargau",
                             prcd = "majoritarian") %$%
  n_seats
